{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_014xRwE8fGArt9kPTj5u2JBF","type":"tool_result","content":"1\t# Session Issues Log — 2026-04-02 (Session 10)\n2\t\n3\t### 4-1-agent-dispatch-module-sdk-integration — verification (2026-04-02T20:00)\n4\t\n5\t- **codeharness verify precondition failures**: sprint-state.json caches stale test/coverage results. Actual live run (27 passed, 100% coverage) confirms ACs.\n6\t- **AGENTS.md stale**: missing entries for agent-dispatch.ts and agent-resolver.ts.\n7\t- **bare:true mapping**: Implementation maps to permissionMode: 'bypassPermissions'. Correct per SDK API.\n8\t\n9\t## Token Report\n10\t- Total tool calls: 12\n11\t- By tool: Bash: 7, Read: 3, Grep: 1, Write: 1\n12\t\n13\t### 4-2-session-boundary-management — create-story (2026-04-02T20:04)\n14\t\n15\t- **Risks:** All ACs test-provable but true E2E session behavior only testable in story 5-1.\n16\t\n17\t## Token Report\n18\t- Total tool calls: 13\n19\t- By tool: Read: 8, Glob: 3, Grep: 1, Bash: 1, Write: 1\n20\t\n21\t### 4-2-session-boundary-management — dev-story (2026-04-02T20:09)\n22\t\n23\tNone.\n24\t\n25\t## Token Report\n26\t- Total tool calls: 16\n27\t- By tool: Bash: 3, Read: 8, Edit: 3, Write: 2, Glob: 2, Skill: 1\n28\t\n29\t### 4-2-session-boundary-management — code-review (2026-04-02T20:13)\n30\t\n31\t**Bugs found and fixed (all MEDIUM):**\n32\t- `resolveSessionId` — unknown boundary fell through to continue (should default to fresh)\n33\t- `recordSessionId` — no validation on empty sessionId\n34\t- `getLastSessionId` — falsy check conflated empty string with undefined\n35\t- Misleading docstring on recordSessionId\n36\t\n37\t**Architecture concern:** recordSessionId creates full TaskCheckpoint entries — risk of duplicates when story 5-1 workflow engine also creates checkpoints.\n38\t\n39\t## Token Report\n40\t- Total tool calls: 18\n41\t- By tool: Bash: 5, Read: 8, Edit: 7, Grep: 2, Glob: 2, Skill: 1\n42\t\n43\t### 4-2-session-boundary-management — verification (2026-04-02T20:16)\n44\t\n45\t- `codeharness verify` failed on AGENTS.md staleness precondition (missing entries for agent-dispatch.ts, agent-resolver.ts, session-manager.ts). Doc-gate, not code issue.\n46\t- All 9 ACs verified via tests. 100% coverage on session-manager.ts. 3858/3858 tests pass.\n47\t\n48\t## Token Report\n49\t- Total tool calls: 10\n50\t- By tool: Bash: 7, Read: 2, Write: 1\n51\t"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"a1f3179e-0b63-4a22-aa4b-b755c26a5a4c","uuid":"6fececac-ba94-4905-8ef1-89d59c03f179","timestamp":"2026-04-02T20:25:35.212Z","tool_use_result":{"type":"text","file":{"filePath":"/Users/ivintik/dev/personal/codeharness/_bmad-output/implementation-artifacts/.session-issues.md","content":"# Session Issues Log — 2026-04-02 (Session 10)\n\n### 4-1-agent-dispatch-module-sdk-integration — verification (2026-04-02T20:00)\n\n- **codeharness verify precondition failures**: sprint-state.json caches stale test/coverage results. Actual live run (27 passed, 100% coverage) confirms ACs.\n- **AGENTS.md stale**: missing entries for agent-dispatch.ts and agent-resolver.ts.\n- **bare:true mapping**: Implementation maps to permissionMode: 'bypassPermissions'. Correct per SDK API.\n\n## Token Report\n- Total tool calls: 12\n- By tool: Bash: 7, Read: 3, Grep: 1, Write: 1\n\n### 4-2-session-boundary-management — create-story (2026-04-02T20:04)\n\n- **Risks:** All ACs test-provable but true E2E session behavior only testable in story 5-1.\n\n## Token Report\n- Total tool calls: 13\n- By tool: Read: 8, Glob: 3, Grep: 1, Bash: 1, Write: 1\n\n### 4-2-session-boundary-management — dev-story (2026-04-02T20:09)\n\nNone.\n\n## Token Report\n- Total tool calls: 16\n- By tool: Bash: 3, Read: 8, Edit: 3, Write: 2, Glob: 2, Skill: 1\n\n### 4-2-session-boundary-management — code-review (2026-04-02T20:13)\n\n**Bugs found and fixed (all MEDIUM):**\n- `resolveSessionId` — unknown boundary fell through to continue (should default to fresh)\n- `recordSessionId` — no validation on empty sessionId\n- `getLastSessionId` — falsy check conflated empty string with undefined\n- Misleading docstring on recordSessionId\n\n**Architecture concern:** recordSessionId creates full TaskCheckpoint entries — risk of duplicates when story 5-1 workflow engine also creates checkpoints.\n\n## Token Report\n- Total tool calls: 18\n- By tool: Bash: 5, Read: 8, Edit: 7, Grep: 2, Glob: 2, Skill: 1\n\n### 4-2-session-boundary-management — verification (2026-04-02T20:16)\n\n- `codeharness verify` failed on AGENTS.md staleness precondition (missing entries for agent-dispatch.ts, agent-resolver.ts, session-manager.ts). Doc-gate, not code issue.\n- All 9 ACs verified via tests. 100% coverage on session-manager.ts. 3858/3858 tests pass.\n\n## Token Report\n- Total tool calls: 10\n- By tool: Bash: 7, Read: 2, Write: 1\n","numLines":51,"startLine":1,"totalLines":51}}}
