lt to fresh)","-- `recordSessionId` — no validation on empty sessionId","-- `getLastSessionId` — falsy check conflated empty string with undefined","-- Misleading docstring on recordSessionId","-","-**Architecture concern:** recordSessionId creates full TaskCheckpoint entries — risk of duplicates when story 5-1 workflow engine also creates checkpoints.","-","-## Token Report","-- Total tool calls: 18","-- By tool: Bash: 5, Read: 8, Edit: 7, Grep: 2, Glob: 2, Skill: 1","-","-### 4-2-session-boundary-management — verification (2026-04-02T20:16)","-","-- `codeharness verify` failed on AGENTS.md staleness precondition (missing entries for agent-dispatch.ts, agent-resolver.ts, session-manager.ts). Doc-gate, not code issue.","-- All 9 ACs verified via tests. 100% coverage on session-manager.ts. 3858/3858 tests pass.","-","-## Token Report","-- Total tool calls: 10","-- By tool: Bash: 7, Read: 2, Write: 1","+# Session Issues Log — 2026-04-03"]}],"originalFile":"# Session Issues Log — 2026-04-02 (Session 10)\n\n### 4-1-agent-dispatch-module-sdk-integration — verification (2026-04-02T20:00)\n\n- **codeharness verify precondition failures**: sprint-state.json caches stale test/coverage results. Actual live run (27 passed, 100% coverage) confirms ACs.\n- **AGENTS.md stale**: missing entries for agent-dispatch.ts and agent-resolver.ts.\n- **bare:true mapping**: Implementation maps to permissionMode: 'bypassPermissions'. Correct per SDK API.\n\n## Token Report\n- Total tool calls: 12\n- By tool: Bash: 7, Read: 3, Grep: 1, Write: 1\n\n### 4-2-session-boundary-management — create-story (2026-04-02T20:04)\n\n- **Risks:** All ACs test-provable but true E2E session behavior only testable in story 5-1.\n\n## Token Report\n- Total tool calls: 13\n- By tool: Read: 8, Glob: 3, Grep: 1, Bash: 1, Write: 1\n\n### 4-2-session-boundary-management — dev-story (2026-04-02T20:09)\n\nNone.\n\n## Token Report\n- Total tool calls: 16\n- By tool: Bash: 3, Read: 8, Edit: 3, Write: 2, Glob: 2, Skill: 1\n\n### 4-2-session-boundary-management — code-review (2026-04-02T20:13)\n\n**Bugs found and fixed (all MEDIUM):**\n- `resolveSessionId` — unknown boundary fell through to continue (should default to fresh)\n- `recordSessionId` — no validation on empty sessionId\n- `getLastSessionId` — falsy check conflated empty string with undefined\n- Misleading docstring on recordSessionId\n\n**Architecture concern:** recordSessionId creates full TaskCheckpoint entries — risk of duplicates when story 5-1 workflow engine also creates checkpoints.\n\n## Token Report\n- Total tool calls: 18\n- By tool: Bash: 5, Read: 8, Edit: 7, Grep: 2, Glob: 2, Skill: 1\n\n### 4-2-session-boundary-management — verification (2026-04-02T20:16)\n\n- `codeharness verify` failed on AGENTS.md staleness precondition (missing entries for agent-dispatch.ts, agent-resolver.ts, session-manager.ts). Doc-gate, not code issue.\n- All 9 ACs verified via tests. 100% coverage on session-manager.ts. 3858/3858 tests pass.\n\n## Token Report\n- Total tool calls: 10\n- By tool: Bash: 7, Read: 2, Write: 1\n"}}
